Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你就是傳聞中變化無常的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會用奇怪的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  只是昏過去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人  到底是誰的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冷靜的人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無故挑起事端的笨蛋的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪種呢  佐倉杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在哪裡見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不透你的牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要讓我忠告多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟愚蠢到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過很多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對笨蛋我是不擇手段的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小炎  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  她有什麼企圖是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉美炎  你難道是…
